defaultAbout the Local Government defaultAssociationdefault&#xa0;
defaultThe 
defaultLocal Government Association (LGA)
default is the national voice of local government.  We work with councils to support, promote and improve local government.
default&#xa0;
defaultWe are a politically-led, cross party organisation which works on behalf of councils to
default ensure local government has a strong, credible voice with national government.  We aim to influence and set the political agenda on the issues that matter to councils so they are able to deliver local solutions to national problems.
default&#xa0;
defaultThe LGA
default covers every 
defaultpart of 
defaultEngland
default and 
defaultWales
default, supporting local government as the most efficient and accountable part of the public sector.
